TITLE
	MD++
Aladip solvated, truncated octahedron box (NTB=-1)
Same topology/configuration as aladip_solvated (NTB=1); only BOUNDCOND differs.
gromosXX converts the BOX block via truncoct_triclinic_box + rotates all
positions/velocities via truncoct_triclinic, then uses the triclinic
(while-loop z->y->x) nearest_image. Reference for PLAN 1.4 / FUTURE Dim 11
NVE run for energy conservation check.

	energy trajectory
END
ENEVERSION
	2023-04-15
END
